message: I'm doing a mock up interview in Arabic for embedded software engineers and for game developers including software engineering positions at top tier companies. I have been working in Europe for seven year, have been interviewed by Google and Qualcomm, I also worked for Qualcomm for a couple of years. The session costs 500le for three hours mock up interview. It will be held in skype. For interested candidates take a look at my website www.Ahmed-tolba.online
